OL,3,CUtility companies dug up NI roads
OL,4,C55,000 times in a year, report finds
OL,6,FComptroller and Auditor General
OL,7,FDorinnia Carville said the Department
OL,8,Ffor Infrastructure is failing to meet
OL,9,Fits inspection and testing targets
OL,10,Fwhen roads and streets are repaired
OL,11,Fafter being dug up by utility
OL,12,Fcompanies.
OL,14,FTo maintain and enhance their
OL,15,Fservices, companies such as those that
OL,16,Fprovide gas, electricity and
OL,17,Fcommunications services, regularly
OL,18,Fopen the road network.
