OL,3,CUtility companies dug up NI roads
OL,4,C55,000 times in a year, report finds
OL,6,FThe report said the key driver for the
OL,7,Fincrease in the number of road
OL,8,Fopenings in recent years is the rise
OL,9,Fin the number of new internet and home
OL,10,Fenergy options for consumers.
OL,12,FIt is the responsibility of the
OL,13,Fcompanies to ensure that, when work is
OL,14,Fcompleted, the road or footpath is
OL,15,Freinstated to an acceptable standard,
OL,16,Fthe Audit Office said.
OL,18,FThe report said that failure to do so
OL,19,Fincreases the risk of accelerated
OL,20,Fdeterioration in the condition of the
OL,21,Froad.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/12
