OL,3,CUtility companies dug up NI roads
OL,4,C55,000 times in a year, report finds
OL,6,FIt said that this risk is growing with
OL,7,Fa rise in the total number of road
OL,8,Fopenings by utility companies, which
OL,9,Fhave been increasing year-on-year for
OL,10,Fthe past seven years, reaching a total
OL,11,Fof 55,000 openings in 2023-24.
OL,13,FIt added: "Despite this increase, the
OL,14,Fdepartment is unable to provide an
OL,15,Festimate of the total proportion of
OL,16,Fstructural maintenance works linked to
OL,17,Fpoor-quality reinstatements by
OL,18,Futilities."
