OL,6,FThe report said defects have to be
OL,7,Fidentified within a two to three-year
OL,8,Fwarranty period to ensure that costs
OL,9,Ffor any remedial works lie with the
OL,10,Fcompanies, rather than taxpayers.
OL,12,FHowever, it said that over the last
OL,13,Fsix years, the department has been
OL,14,Funable to meet its target of
OL,15,Finspecting 30% of total openings.
