OL,6,FThe report said the Stormont
OL,7,Fdepartment's current testing regime
OL,8,Fconsisted of a high number of visual
OL,9,Finspections, along with a small volume
OL,10,Fof core tests involving laboratory
OL,11,Ftesting of samples taken from
OL,12,Freinstatements.
OL,14,FIt pointed out there is a divergence
OL,15,Fin performance in tests measured by
OL,16,Fvisual inspections versus core sample
OL,17,Ftesting.
