OL,3,CUtility companies dug up NI roads
OL,4,C55,000 times in a year, report finds
OL,6,FThe report said: "While the pass rate
OL,7,Ffor visual inspections is above a
OL,8,Ftarget of 90%, the more detailed core
OL,9,Fsample tests are reporting failure
OL,10,Frates well above the target of 10%."
OL,12,FIt also said inspections are based on
OL,13,Frandom selection, rather than on a
OL,14,Frisk-based model based upon historic
OL,15,Fresults or current testing models in
OL,16,Fother UK regions.
